#

Chicken Stir-Fry with Broccoli and Peppers

25 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthyStir-Fry

Description

A vibrant and colorful chicken stir-fry packed with tender chicken, crunchy broccoli, and sweet bell peppers, all tossed in a savory sauce.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 1 pound
  • broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • bell peppers (mixed colors): 1 cup
  • soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • ginger (grated): 1 tablespoon
  • sesame oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cornstarch: 1 tablespoon
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • green onions (sliced, for garnish): 1/4 cup
